    <item>
      <title>流动性担忧加剧加密货币价格压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/liquidity-concerns-help-to-fuel-crypto-price-pressures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最近的加密资产抛售正在考验行业公理，即比特币相当于“数字黄金”，因此属于资产组合以对冲股市波动，这种情况很少见。Delta Blockchain Fund 的 Kavita Gupta 与 Sonali Basak 和 Michael Regan 就“Bloomberg Crypto”进行了交谈。（来源：Bloomberg）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/liquidity-concerns-help-to-fuel-crypto-price-pressures</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 19:55:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
